data.description: #267888. SURPRISING ONE-LEVEL SPACIOUS RANCH OFFERS PRIVACY IN ITS SETTING WITH PLENTY OF OFF-STREET PARKING FOR EVERYONE.  Family time 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms - Surprising spacious master suite-ensuite-walk in closet. Entertainment with Great Room contemporary country with expansive kitchen island and serving buffet, pantry, convenient powder room and 2 Covered Attached Patios.  Oversized Laundry Room. Parking: Room For RV and Toys, Space for your Business Trucks and Trailers along with a 6 bay garage which offers 12’ ceilings and 10’ entry garage doors, including rear garage door thru entry to backyard with an additional cement parking slab. Unique Location sets you up for privacy and security a must see. NOTE: Just under $100,000 in upgrades were added above the original purchase price...:)
